Khelldon - Let's find all flagstone and cobble stone blocks and make sure they need Mortar for repair.
The game still doesn't allow for more than one upgrade item so we'll leave that unchanged.
-->

<!-- Add mortar to the repair items of the two masters, these will append throughout all flagstone amnd cobblestone blocks -->
